# Helm chart templates — these are Go-template-flavoured YAML, not pure
# YAML. Prettier's YAML parser rejects the `{{- if }}` directives and the
# multi-doc layout (manifests separated by `---` without a leading
# document separator in helm templates). `helm lint` + the chart-lint
# CI gate (.github/workflows/chart-lint.yml) is the authority.
